WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Welcome to a visual-first learning lesson built for caption clarity.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Learners can read each caption outside the video and revisit any line.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:11.000
This approach reduces overload and makes key ideas easier to follow.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Transcript navigation supports self-paced review during class or homework.
